{
  "info": {
    "name": "Transaction API - Prueba Tecnica Fullstack (Local)",
    "description": "Coleccion estatica apuntando a un entorno local levantado con ./scripts/run.sh (http://localhost:8090). Solo hay que importarla, no requiere seleccionar ningun entorno ni configurar variables. Incluye casos de exito y de error (404/422/429), y scripts de test automaticos (pm.test) que validan cada respuesta y encadenan variables internas entre requests (por ejemplo, el id de una transaccion creada se reutiliza solo en 'Get Transaction by ID'). Esos scripts usan la API pm.* de Postman; al importar en Insomnia las requests funcionan igual, pero esos scripts no se ejecutan (Insomnia no los soporta). Para probar contra la demo en produccion en vez de local, usa postman_collection.production.json.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "transaction_id",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "used_idempotency_key",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "assistant_log_id",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "rpa_extraction_id",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 200', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "pm.test('status ok', function () { pm.expect(pm.response.json().status).to.eql('ok'); });"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:8090/health",
              "host": [
                "localhost"
              ],
              "protocol": "http",
              "port": "8090",
              "path": [
                "health"
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Transacciones",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Transaction (nueva key, 201)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 201', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(201); });",
                  "var body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('trae id y status pending', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(body.id).to.be.a('string');",
                  "    pm.expect(body.status).to.eql('pending');",
                  "});",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('transaction_id', body.id);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('used_idempotency_key', body.idempotency_key);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:8090/api/v1/transactions/create",
              "host": [
                "localhost"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "transactions",
                "create"
              ],
              "protocol": "http",
              "port": "8090"
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"user_id\": \"user-1\",\n  \"monto\": 150.5,\n  \"tipo\": \"deposito\",\n  \"idempotency_key\": \"{{$guid}}\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Transaction (repite key, 200)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 200 (idempotente)', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(200); });",
                  "pm.test('devuelve el mismo id que la transaccion original', function () {",
                  "    pm.expect(pm.response.json().id).to.eql(pm.collectionVariables.get('transaction_id'));",
                  "});"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:8090/api/v1/transactions/create",
              "host": [
                "localhost"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "transactions",
                "create"
              ],
              "protocol": "http",
              "port": "8090"
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"user_id\": \"user-1\",\n  \"monto\": 150.5,\n  \"tipo\": \"deposito\",\n  \"idempotency_key\": \"{{used_idempotency_key}}\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "Corre esta request DESPUES de 'Create Transaction (nueva key, 201)' -- reutiliza la misma idempotency_key que quedo guardada en la variable de coleccion used_idempotency_key, para demostrar la idempotencia real."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Transaction (monto invalido, 422)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 422', function () { pm.response.to.have.status(422); });"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://localhost:8090/api/v1/transactions/create",
              "host": [
                "localhost"
              ],
              "path": [
                "api",
                "v1",
                "transactions",
                "create"
              ],
              "protocol": "http",
              "port": "8090"
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"user_id\": \"user-1\",\n  \"monto\": -10,\n  \"tipo\": \"deposito\",\n  \"idempotency_key\": \"{{$guid}}\"\n}"
            },
            "description": "monto negativo viola la validacion de Pydantic (ge=0.01)."
          }
        },
